definitions.definition: A type of motor vehicle designed to move on the ground under its own stored power and intended to carry a driver , a small number of additional passengers , and a very limited amount of other load. A car or motorcar .
definitions.label_groups: US , Canada , Philippines , Australia , New Zealand

main_definition: ( US , Canada , Philippines , Australia , New Zealand ) A type of motor vehicle designed to move on the ground under its own stored power and intended to carry a driver , a small number of additional passengers , and a very limited amount of other load. A car or motorcar .
